reviewText: it was in good condition I liked it

This series is the neatest of the el hazard seasons. The disc is hard to get and if you can find it will probably set you back about 40 dollars. the others in the series are about 3 to 6 dollars each but getting this one is crucial to understanding the series. why its so expensive we will never know but get it from a reputable seller as it is prime for unscroupulos sellers to gouge you.
